PN,33401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1784809126
OL,3,CStudent struggled in river waiting for
OL,4,Chelp for 20 minutes before death
OL,6,FA York student who drowned in the
OL,7,FRiver Ouse floated above the water for
OL,8,F20 minutes waiting for help before he
OL,9,Fdied, an inquest has heard.
OL,11,FEvan d'Andilly, 19 and from
OL,12,FScunthorpe, went into the River Ouse
OL,13,Fin York on 5 March 2025. He had been
OL,14,Fout in the city centre drinking with
OL,15,Fhis friends.
OL,17,FEmergency services were called at
OL,18,Faround 3am to reports of a man in the
OL,19,Fwater between Ouse Bridge and
OL,20,FSkeldergate Bridge.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1784809126
OL,3,CStudent struggled in river waiting for
OL,4,Chelp for 20 minutes before death
OL,6,FAn inquest into his death heard Evan
OL,7,Ftried to float for 20 minutes but
OL,8,Fpolice were unable to reach him with a
OL,9,Fthrow line.
OL,11,FHe slipped under the water before a
OL,12,Frescue boat reached the scene. Evan's
OL,13,Fbody was recovered later that morning.
OL,15,FThe coroner concluded Evan's cause of
OL,16,Fdeath was drowning as a result of
OL,17,Fimmersion in the water.
OL,19,FEvan's dad, Gordon d'Andilly, said:
OL,20,F"He was a strong swimmer. There's no
OL,21,Firony to it.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1784809126
OL,3,CStudent struggled in river waiting for
OL,4,Chelp for 20 minutes before death
OL,6,F"They said in court that on average
OL,7,F(someone would survive) five to seven
OL,8,Fminutes. Evan lasted nearly 20 minutes
OL,9,Fwhich is a credit to him. He fought to
OL,10,Fthe end and I'm proud of him.
OL,12,F"My beautiful Evan. Life changed
OL,13,Fforever when he died. I don't laugh as
OL,14,Feasily. I cry more. I'm forever
OL,15,Fchanged."
OL,17,FNorth Yorkshire Fire and Rescue
OL,18,FService's nearest rescue boat is
OL,19,Fstationed in Selby. Mr d'Andilly
OL,20,Fbelieves his son may not have died if
OL,21,Fthe resources were closer to York.
OL,26,@oD@ApmoD@Wpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1784809126
OL,3,CStudent struggled in river waiting for
OL,4,Chelp for 20 minutes before death
OL,6,FHe said: "In regard to the response of
OL,7,Fthe emergency services, I have got
OL,8,Fnothing but praise and thanks. In
OL,9,Fregard to the resources available, my
OL,10,Fopinion differs.
OL,12,F"It's become apparent that the
OL,13,Fresources that the police understood
OL,14,Fwere available aren't there. The
OL,15,FYorkshire rescue boat which was
OL,16,Fpreviously in York was decommissioned
OL,17,Fa number of years before. Since that
OL,18,Fdecommissioning I have understood
OL,19,Fthere's been a spike in deaths in York.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1784809126
OL,3,CStudent struggled in river waiting for
OL,4,Chelp for 20 minutes before death
OL,6,F"I hope lessons can be learned and
OL,7,Fthis inquest will have served its
OL,8,Fpurpose preventing further families
OL,9,Ffrom having to go through what we have
OL,10,Fhad to."
OL,12,FIn response, North Yorkshire Fire and
OL,13,FRescue Service said: "Our thoughts
OL,14,Fremain with the family and friends of
OL,15,FEvan d'Andilly following the
OL,16,Fconclusion of the inquest into his
OL,17,Fdeath.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1784809126
OL,3,CStudent struggled in river waiting for
OL,4,Chelp for 20 minutes before death
OL,6,F"We remain committed to working with
OL,7,Four partners to learn from incidents,
OL,8,Freduce risk and help keep people safe
OL,9,Faround North Yorkshire and York's
OL,10,Frivers and waterways.
OL,12,F"North Yorkshire Fire and Rescue
OL,13,FService operates six Swift Water
OL,14,FRescue stations and a powered rescue
OL,15,Fboat based in Selby, with resources
OL,16,Fpositioned across the county to
OL,17,Frespond to flooding and water rescue
OL,18,Femergencies.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1784809126
OL,3,CStudent struggled in river waiting for
OL,4,Chelp for 20 minutes before death
OL,6,F"In York, we have recently enhanced
OL,7,Four provision through additional
OL,8,Fbankside extended pole and reach lines
OL,9,Fand the imminent rollout of Fast
OL,10,FRescue Deployment Devices to York and
OL,11,FAcomb stations. Together with the
OL,12,Fspecialist capabilities provided by
OL,13,FYork Rescue Boat in conjunction with
OL,14,Fthe Service, these improvements
OL,15,Fstrengthen the response available
OL,16,Falong the city's waterways."
OL,18,FEvan's mother, Lorraine d'Andilly,
OL,19,Fsaid: "I replay those 20 minutes (in
OL,20,Fmy head) over and over - it's torture.
OL,26,@{D@bpm|D@Hpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1784809126
OL,3,CStudent struggled in river waiting for
OL,4,Chelp for 20 minutes before death
OL,6,F"No finding today can ever lessen the
OL,7,Fpain of losing him or undo the
OL,8,Fdevastation that our family has
OL,9,Fendured.
OL,11,F"But acknowledging what went wrong is
OL,12,Fan essential step towards
OL,13,Faccountability and more importantly
OL,14,Ffrom preventing another family from
OL,15,Fexperiencing the same heartbreak.
OL,17,F"He was an awesome human being - kind,
OL,18,Floving, generous and incredibly funny.
OL,19,FHe brought joy to so many people and
OL,20,Fhe is deeply loved and deeply missed
OL,21,Fevery single day.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1784809126
OL,3,CStudent struggled in river waiting for
OL,4,Chelp for 20 minutes before death
OL,6,F"He filled our lives with laughter and
OL,7,Fhis death has left a space that can
OL,8,Fnever be filled. He had so much life
OL,9,Fahead of him and he should still be
OL,10,Fwith us today."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
